.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: go, scrabble
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, epic
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | go    | scrabble |
| Flower         | azalea        | iris  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | epic   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

